<bibRefCitation author="Tyler" etAl="et al." firstAuthor="Tyler" pageId="27" pageNumber="28" pagination="175 - 194" refId="ref203064" refString="Tyler, P. A., Emson, R. H., Sumida, P. &amp; Howell, K. (2005) Ophiuroid distribution at sublittoral and bathyal depths round the Faroe Islands, NE Atlantic Ocean. BIOFAR Proceedings, 2005, 175 - 194." type="journal article" year="2005">
